      <title>星巴克聘请首位中国区增长官以促进销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/starbucks-hires-first-china-growth-officer-to-boost-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星巴克公司聘请了其首位中国首席增长官，负责吸引年轻的咖啡消费者回归，因为这家美国连锁店在其最大的国际市场上正面临着价格更便宜的本地竞争对手的冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/starbucks-hires-first-china-growth-officer-to-boost-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 05:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
